                "invention-title": [
                    "Water electrolysis hydrogen drying system and method thereof",
                    "一种水电解氢气干燥系统及其方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a water electrolysis hydrogen drying system and a method thereof.The water electrolysis hydrogen drying system comprises a gas inlet pipe opening, a product gas outlet, a first adsorption tower and a second adsorption tower, the first adsorption tower and the second adsorption tower are connected between the gas inlet pipe opening and the product gas outlet, and the adsorption periods of the first adsorption tower and the second adsorption tower are switched at intervals to be used, so that in any adsorption period, the product gas is separated from the product gas outlet. When one adsorption tower is in an adsorption state, the other adsorption tower is in a heating regeneration or cooling state; when hydrogen enters the gas inlet pipe orifice, part of hydrogen enters the adsorption tower in an adsorption state, is dried by an adsorbent in the adsorption tower and then flows out from the gas outlet end of the adsorption tower, so that the dried hydrogen flows out from the product gas outlet; the other part of hydrogen enters a heater to be heated, and the heated hydrogen enters the adsorption tower in a heating regeneration state, so that water on the adsorbent flows out of the gas outlet end of the adsorption tower along with the heated hydrogen in a water vapor form; the equipment manufacturing cost is reduced, the process is simplified, and invalid heat loss is avoided."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种水电解氢气干燥系统及其方法，包括进气管口、产品气出口、连接于进气管口与产品气出口之间的第一吸附塔以及第二吸附塔，且第一吸附塔与第二吸附塔的吸附周期呈间隔切换使用，以使任一吸附周期内，当其中一吸附塔处于吸附状态时，另一吸附塔处于加热再生或冷却状态；当氢气进入进气管口时，部分氢气进入处于吸附状态的吸附塔中，并经吸附塔内的吸附剂干燥后从吸附塔的出气端流出，使得干燥后的氢气由产品气出口处流出；另一部分氢气进入加热器进行加热，加热后的氢气进入处于加热再生状态的吸附塔中，使得吸附剂上的水分以水蒸气形式随加热后的氢气一同从吸附塔的出气端流出；本发明降低设备制造成本，简化流程，避免热量无效损失。"
                }
            ]
